static void Mailbox_boxEmptyISRBss ( uintptr_t  arg)
static

Description
The function is the registered ISR for the "mailbox empty" interrupt for BSS remote endpoint. This interrupt indicates that an acknowledge for the last write operation was received.

Parameters
[in]argArgument which is registered with the OS while registering the ISR
Return values
Notapplicable
